# MDView - Single File Version

This is a completely self-contained markdown viewer that requires **only one file** - `md.html`.

## Features

✅ **Single File** - No external dependencies  
✅ **Drag & Drop** - Drop markdown files directly  
✅ **File Picker** - Click to browse and select files  
✅ **GitHub Flavored Markdown** - Full markdown support  
✅ **Responsive Design** - Works on all devices  
✅ **No Installation** - Just open in any browser  

## Usage

1. **Download** `md.html` to your computer
2. **Open** `md.html` in any web browser (double-click or drag to browser)
3. **Use** - Drag markdown files onto the page or click "Choose File"

## Browser Compatibility

Works in all modern browsers:
- Chrome ✅
- Firefox ✅  
- Safari ✅
- Edge ✅

## File Size

343KB (includes all CSS and JavaScript)

---

*Built with React, Create React App, and GitHub Flavored Markdown*
